  "text": "Leucine has been shown to stimulate insulin secretion, and the restoration of muscle protein synthesis in ageing rats could originate indirectly through an increase of plasma insulinaemia. This could not explain the results in our experiment [CITATION_1] since the kinetics of insulinaemia were not significantly different in the rats fed the control and the leucine-supplemented meals.",
